en.title: FE Welcomes QP Wearer, San Juan City Mayor, JV Ejercito!
en.content: (Left-Right) San Juan City Councilor Francisco Zamora (Son of Congressman Ronaldo Zamora) , FE Philippines Country Licensee Jeremy Looi, San Juan City Mayor Honorable. Joseph Victor Ejercito (Son of Former President Joseph Ejercito Estrada) and FE Spokeman Allan "Triggerman" Caidic.
